responseText: NSLOCTEXT("", "DEAE67434EF6E9BB0945BB80428E5B55", "The cargo wagon has taken great damage. An attached sign reads: Athenaeum No. 12. It\'s scorched marked are unlike most battle scars of the region. A demonic sigil has been painted upon it with blood. Some of the cargo is missing.")
